posts.post_content:
Only gonna have these out there for a week or so, and then I’ll pull them….

Have had these socked away for a few months now, figured it’s Likely time to let these go. Obviously super difficult to find these, and comps are not really available…..or at least not current. Nice thing about these is no back loss….

I’m available via PM to discuss.

Thanks for looking!
Jeff
